config DVFS
	bool "DVFS support"
	depends on REGULATOR_AXP803 || REGULATOR_SY8106A
	help
		Enable control of the ARM CPU frequency at runtime. Do
		not select this option if you have a native DVFS driver
		in Linux, or if you have any other Linux driver that may
		attempt to communicate with the PMIC at runtime.
